# Online Complaint Management System - Implementation Plan

A full-stack web application for citizens to submit and track complaints to police, with an admin panel for officers to manage, update, and resolve them.

## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph LR
    A[React Frontend<br>Netlify] --> B[FastAPI Backend<br>Vercel]
    B --> C[Supabase<br>PostgreSQL + Auth]
```

| Layer | Technology | Hosting |
|-------|-----------|---------|
| Frontend | React 18 + Vite | Netlify |
| Backend | Python FastAPI | Vercel |
| Database & Auth | Supabase | Supabase Cloud |

---

## Database Schema (Supabase)

### Tables

**`profiles`** — extends Supabase auth.users
| Column | Type | Notes |
|--------|------|-------|
| id | uuid (PK, FK → auth.users) | |
| full_name | text | |
| phone | text | |
| role | text | `citizen` or `admin` |
| created_at | timestamptz | |

**`complaints`**
| Column | Type | Notes |
|--------|------|-------|
| id | uuid (PK) | |
| user_id | uuid (FK → profiles) | |
| tracking_id | text (unique) | e.g. `CMP-2026-00042` |
| category | text | Theft, Fraud, Cybercrime, etc. |
| subject | text | |
| description | text | |
| location | text | |
| status | text | `pending` / `in_review` / `investigating` / `resolved` / `rejected` |
| priority | text | `low` / `medium` / `high` / `critical` |
| admin_remarks | text | |
| created_at | timestamptz | |
| updated_at | timestamptz | |

---

## Frontend (React + Vite)

### Project Structure
```
frontend/
├── public/
├── src/
│   ├── assets/
│   ├── components/     (Navbar, Footer, Sidebar, ProtectedRoute, StatusBadge...)
│   ├── contexts/       (AuthContext.jsx)
│   ├── pages/
│   │   ├── Landing.jsx
│   │   ├── Login.jsx
│   │   ├── Register.jsx
│   │   ├── UserDashboard.jsx
│   │   ├── SubmitComplaint.jsx
│   │   ├── TrackComplaint.jsx
│   │   ├── ComplaintDetail.jsx
│   │   ├── AdminDashboard.jsx
│   │   ├── AdminComplaints.jsx
│   │   └── AdminComplaintDetail.jsx
│   ├── lib/            (supabaseClient.js, api.js)
│   ├── styles/         (index.css — full design system)
│   ├── App.jsx
│   └── main.jsx
├── index.html
├── netlify.toml
└── vite.config.js
```

### Pages

| Page | Route | Purpose |
|------|-------|---------|
| Landing | `/` | Hero, features, CTA |
| Login | `/login` | Email + password |
| Register | `/register` | Sign up as citizen |
| User Dashboard | `/dashboard` | My complaints overview |
| Submit Complaint | `/submit` | Form with category, location, description |
| Track Complaint | `/track` | Search by tracking ID |
| Complaint Detail | `/complaint/:id` | Full detail + status timeline |
| Admin Dashboard | `/admin` | Stats cards, recent complaints |
| Admin Complaints | `/admin/complaints` | Full list with filters |
| Admin Detail | `/admin/complaint/:id` | Update status, priority, remarks |

### Design Theme
- **Dark professional theme** with deep navy/charcoal base (`#0f172a`, `#1e293b`)
- **Accent**: Vibrant blue-purple gradient (`#6366f1` → `#8b5cf6`)
- **Status colors**: Green (resolved), amber (in_review), red (rejected), blue (investigating)
- **Font**: Google Fonts "Inter" for body, "Outfit" for headings
- **Glass-morphism** cards with subtle backdrop-blur
- **Micro-animations** on hover, status transitions, page loads
- **Fully responsive** via CSS media queries + flexbox/grid

---

## Backend (Python FastAPI)

### Project Structure
```
backend/
├── main.py            (FastAPI app, CORS, routes)
├── database.py        (Supabase client init)
├── routes/
│   ├── auth.py        (register, login, profile)
│   ├── complaints.py  (CRUD for citizens)
│   └── admin.py       (admin-only endpoints)
├── requirements.txt
└── vercel.json
```

### API Endpoints

| Method | Path | Auth | Purpose |
|--------|------|------|---------|
| POST | `/api/auth/register` | — | Register new citizen |
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | — | Login |
| GET | `/api/auth/profile` | User | Get profile |
| POST | `/api/complaints` | User | Submit complaint |
| GET | `/api/complaints` | User | List my complaints |
| GET | `/api/complaints/:id` | User | Get complaint detail |
| GET | `/api/complaints/track/:trackingId` | — | Public tracking |
| GET | `/api/admin/complaints` | Admin | List all complaints |
| GET | `/api/admin/stats` | Admin | Dashboard statistics |
| PATCH | `/api/admin/complaints/:id` | Admin | Update status/priority/remarks |

